metadata.name: Freelancer's Dream in a Coffeehouse
metadata.description:
Just imagine for a moment! You walked into the coffeehouse and see all these people. I have gathered all of them to invite you for a cup of coffee. 

Try to recognize them first!

Isn't it fun to let your eye wander and take them all in. 

Tried? Check  it here then↘️

Karl Lagerfeld and Marilyn Monroe, Vincent Van Gogh and Elsa Schiaparelli, Twiggy and Salvador Dali,  Andy Warhol and Edie Sedgwick.

Would you like to have a cup of coffee in such company?


Watercolor painting, 29.7 x 42 cm (11.69 x 16.54 inches).
